webscript.description:
Web Script that returns SyncSet Changes (list of source nodeRefs) for the specified ssdId ... for any outstanding sync changes (in the sync audit change log).

The request body will be of the form: 

   GET .../sync/syncsetchanges?ssdId=9319d5a3-03c1-4f86-8b44-f8516ff91820&maxItems=1024

The response body will be of the form: 

   [
      "workspace://SpacesStore/bd9c79fd-dcac-4af9-a1a5-8d3e490ab7c9",
      "workspace://SpacesStore/b171e2f7-fb9d-46a9-822b-b6599886101f",
      "workspace://SpacesStore/235a3817-76a7-4417-8953-1b7d206f4579",
      "workspace://SpacesStore/b23edfe8-be7b-4413-87df-3557290fe3d6"
   ]
